        <td bgColor="black"><textarea cols="70" name="Message" rows="12" wrap="VIRTUAL">[quote]
I cast this on myself, at Max Health, Standing.
I have an innate Regen of 2hp per tic standing.
I wrote down my current HP every tic.
Dotting one's self is subject to PvP rules of 66% damage of Base.

The damage in the white is the current HP i wrote down every tic.
The damage in the [blue][b]blue[/b][/blue] is the damage minus my innate regen of 2hp a tic.
The damage in the [red][b]red[/b][/red] is the damage with the 66% restriction removed.

Tic #1 actually occurs, because i saw my HP fluctuate from 2432 to 2430 back up to 2432 very briefly, and this trend was seen every tic thereafter.


[code]
              Level: 53


[green]        Starting HP: 2432[/green]
[blue]          Ending HP: 1320[/blue]
[blue]       Overall Loss: 1112[/blue]


         Total Tics: 17


[green]     Standing Regen: 2[/green]
[green]   Overall HP Regen: 34[/green]
[blue]Regen Factored Loss: 1146[/blue]


[red][b]PvP Factored Loss: 1528[/b][/red]


[u]Base HP: 2432  [blue](Dam)[/blue] [red](PvP Comp)[/red][/u]


Tic   1: 2432    [blue](2)[/blue]     [red](3)[/red]
Tic   2: 2430    [blue](4)[/blue]     [red](5)[/red]
