Tic   8: 2229   [blue](58)[/blue]    [red](77)[/red]
Tic   9: 2164   [blue](67)[/blue]    [red](89)[/red]
Tic  10: 2090   [blue](76)[/blue]   [red](101)[/red]
Tic  11: 2007   [blue](85)[/blue]   [red](113)[/red]
Tic  12: 1915   [blue](94)[/blue]   [red](125)[/red]
